 way, way bigger, which means that if we don't change anything in terms of scalability, we

00:30:31.480 --> 00:30:35.360
 will be able to do even fewer transactions than we are able to do today.

00:30:35.360 --> 00:30:36.360
 Right.

00:30:36.360 --> 00:30:37.360
 So, yeah.

00:30:37.360 --> 00:30:38.360
 Any thoughts on that?

