 So, I don't like to sound off on things that are not my business…

00:31:01.600 --> 00:31:02.600
 Yeah.

00:31:02.600 --> 00:31:03.600
 Yeah, of course.

00:31:03.600 --> 00:31:04.600
 …get in other people's way.

