 Which is great.

00:34:39.480 --> 00:34:40.480
 That's cool.

00:34:40.480 --> 00:34:41.480
 Yeah.

00:34:41.480 --> 00:34:46.800
 It's a fascinating, surprising thing about blockchains and open permission systems, unlike

00:34:46.800 --> 00:34:51.080
 the previous few decades of software, where basically the devs could do anything they wanted

00:34:51.080 --> 00:34:55.720
 and the users had no choice in the matter, other than stop using that software.

00:34:55.720 --> 00:34:56.720
 Yeah.

