 There's like six or seven funded, skilled, dedicated, Zcash-focused development orgs,

00:35:15.840 --> 00:35:16.680
 which is amazing.

00:35:16.680 --> 00:35:17.680
 Wow.

00:35:17.680 --> 00:35:25.160
 Okay, so imagine, hypothetically, all seven or however many got together and said, "Let's

00:35:25.160 --> 00:35:26.660
 turn off T-addresses."

